nodes.text: Interceptor Two was a squadron of starfighters assigned to the Endurance-class fleet carrier Intrepid of the New Republic Defense Fleet Fifth Battle Group.

Immediately prior to the Battle of Doornik 319, Interceptor Two was one of the squadrons prepared for immediate launch aboard the Intrepid, and when the Intrepid entered the system, Interceptor Two was part of the fleet carrier's fighter screen.
